  "about": {
    "details": "<p>Incorporated in 2014, Dhyaani Tile And Marblez Limited is involved in the business of <strong>trading and producing tiles</strong> for floors, bathrooms, kitchens, balconies, and stairwells. The company offers two categories of products: Double Charge Vitrified Tiles and Glazed Vitrified Tiles. The company warehouse and the physical store are located in Ahmedabad. Dhyaani Tile And Marblez produces rustic, polished glazed, polished, and textured tiles. The company identifies its customer's needs and allows them to choose the perfect design from its wide range of tiles samples. The company has well-known brand suppliers located all over India.</p>\n<p><strong>Competitive Strengths:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Widespread distribution network.</li>\n<li>Experienced management and dedicated employee base.</li>\n<li>Quality assurance.</li>\n<li>Strategically beneficial location.</li>\n</ol>"
  },
